---
import site from '@/lib/site'
---

<section class="section section--tint s3-benefits">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="s3-benefits__intro">
      <h2 class="s3-benefits__heading">Transform Your Skin with Every Session</h2>
      <p class="s3-benefits__sub">Discover why our dermaplaning facial is the perfect solution for anyone seeking brighter, smoother, more radiant skin.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s3-benefits__grid">

      <div class="s3-benefits__item">
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-title"><strong>Instant Smoothness &amp; Glow</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-desc">Remove weeks of dead skin buildup and peach fuzz in a single session. Your complexion looks brighter and feels incredibly smooth from the very first treatment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-benefits__item">
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-title"><strong>Enhanced Product Absorption</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-desc">After dermaplaning, your skincare products penetrate up to 5x deeper into the skin. Your serums, moisturizers, and treatments work harder and deliver better results.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-benefits__item">
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-title"><strong>Flawless Makeup Application</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-desc">Say goodbye to patchy foundation and cakey concealer. Dermaplaning creates a perfectly smooth canvas so makeup glides on evenly and lasts longer.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-benefits__item">
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-title"><strong>Safe &amp; Gentle Process</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-benefits__item-desc">Unlike harsh chemical peels or abrasive scrubs, our dermaplaning facial is gentle enough for all skin types including sensitive skin, with zero downtime required.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s3-benefits__cta">
      <a href={site.calcomUrl} class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Schedule Now</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-benefits__intro {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s3-benefits__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-benefits__sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-benefits__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .s3-benefits__item {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .s3-benefits__item-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .s3-benefits__item-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-benefits__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s3-benefits__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .s3-benefits__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
